{"id": "1396057072780574751", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "今日份杜勒小知识：所谓“食尸鬼”吃尸体的形象其实不存在于原本阿拉伯ghoul的设定中，而是在把一千零一夜和其他ghoul有关故事介绍到西方世界的过程中诞生的产物\n从阿拉伯文翻法文的时候凭空多出来了一个叫Amina的女角色，这位是“陪伴食尸鬼的女巫”，虽然有人类丈夫但经常跑墓地找食尸鬼玩（顺便食尸鬼在墓地徘徊刨尸体吃的设定也是这时候凭空冒出来的）\n然后这个Amina被西方世界广泛接受了，有观点认为皮克曼也是沿这条线捏出来的\n合理怀疑这位就是杜勒pv里“爱侣”的原型", "timestamp": "2025-07-19T09:12:23.637000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1396057310673240085", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "~~这个cv子安武人，弄得我觉也不睡了跑去翻啊翻啊翻（呆）~~", "timestamp": "2025-07-19T09:13:20.355000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1396061391793819669", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1301813973703852035", "author_name": "flarinsidia", "author_bot": false, "content": "另外阿拉伯食尸鬼里有一种叫shiqq的是所谓“半边人”，只有一半的身体可见，不知道是否是杜勒一边眼睛冒鬼火以及这里一边面孔虚化的美术依据\n~~冒鬼火的眼睛左右横跳太难看明白了~~\n哦两边都冒火那当我没说（", "timestamp": "2025-07-19T09:29:33.370000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-19T09:38:10.201000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1396061391252881489", "filename": "468E60C3-5930-44AF-AFC5-D01C9064AC63.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3290287, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1173463482503536711/1396061391252881489/468E60C3-5930-44AF-AFC5-D01C9064AC63.png?ex=6a365d7d&is=6a350bfd&hm=41f8d76ecc359aefc4c61c2657c695640a82f51b2baf0a0b0f81866fb1e3ae57&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
